defaultThe Nuffield Health Bond, launched May 2013, is a five-year fixed-term product, offering a fixed annual return of 6% (gross) in cash, for investments of £1,000 - £250,000. Our initial aim, to raise £15m, was reached early due to a phenomenal response that 
defaultresulted in the Bond being over-subscribed - a gratifying endorsement of the Nuffield Health proposition in a depressed bond market. Ultimately the Bond raised £18m to help us make a real difference to the future of healthcare. 
